00:07:44,369 --> 00:07:47,612
she bound her hands, wore glasses that made it hard for her to see.

150
00:07:47,872 --> 00:07:51,355
And she just explored the world and figured out where things were difficult

151
00:07:51,375 --> 00:07:51,956
for somebody who was

