00:08:48,125 --> 00:08:50,527
real users using his device that he realized

175
00:08:50,547 --> 00:08:51,909
that it was just impractical.

176
00:08:52,309 --> 00:08:54,691
And so what he did was he redesigned his CRT machine,

177
00:08:54,731 --> 00:08:58,014
his imaging machine, so that it was a lot easier and just more

