00:10:14,889 --> 00:10:19,051
is I was trying to find all the different aspects that could implement,

204
00:10:19,091 --> 00:10:21,733
that could be the use cases that people have on STEAM.

205
00:10:22,933 --> 00:10:27,516
So qualitative, again, is a good way to do a springboard for quantitative research.

